The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, gospel, indie, pop, techno
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, car, ship, taxi, van
 1. the photographer is on the left of the fan of country##1
 2. the lawyer is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 3. the fan of gospel is the photographer##1
 4. the fan of country is the lawyer##1
 5. the bartender is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the lawyer##1
 7. the person driving the car is on the right of the pilot##1
 8. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the left of the person eating kale##1
10. the person eating zucchini is the fan of indie##1
11. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
12. the person driving the bike is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food          | plum        | kale       | papaya | lemon   | zucchini  |
| Job   | pilot | bartender | photographer | lawyer   | social-worker |
| Music-Genre   | pop         | techno     | gospel | country | indie     |
| Transport     | bike        | car        | van    | taxi    | ship      |

