 4. the german is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 7. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 9. the german is the person who's sport is cricket##1
10. the turkish is in the middle##1
11. the fan of folk is on the left of the turkish##1
12. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
13. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
14. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |       4       |    5     |
