 2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 3. the japanese is the person driving the car##1
 4. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person driving the tram is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the argentine##1
 8. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 9. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
10. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
11. the german is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
12. the italian is the person drinking tea##1
13. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

