.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda, sprite
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, pop, punk, salsa
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, havana, dunhill, fonseca, montecristo
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, snowmobile, train, tram
 1. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of punk is the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 4. the fan of blues is the montecristo-smoker##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the fan of pop is the havana-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
11. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
12. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
13. the cain-smoker is the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
